column_.text_: Oh boy... This town is nice.

Oh, brother. At least one of us is, that's for sure.

Word is there's a village that runs a mining operation on a nearby
island.
It's got an altar dedicated to—get this—a "primeval god."

An' when this god stirs up a wind, lodes o' ore gets exposed, ripe
for the plucking.
Then this town takes those mined ores to make the finest jewelry.

Anyway, gonna stay put and sniff around for more info. I'll letcha

See ya later, !
